Description: Hit 10 pitch shots from 40m and get at least 2 shots to stop within 3 meters of the hole (Fairway)

Title: Up and Down Fairway
Description: Make 2 up and downs from 20m away in the Fairway (10 attempts)

Title: Longer Bunker Escape
Description: Hit a bunker shot from 25m within 5 meters of the hole

Title: Distance Control Putt 8m
Description: Get 3 balls to stop within 0.5m past the hole from 8 meters

Title: Amateur Approach 100m
Description: Pick a target 100m away. Hit a ball left of the target, and make sure it finishes no more than 15 meters left of the target

Title: Amateur Approach 110m
Description: Pick a target 110m away. Hit a ball right of the target, and make sure it finishes no more than 20 meters right of the target

Title: Amateur Approach 120m
Description: Pick a target 120m away. Hit a ball left of the target, and make sure it finishes no more than 20 meters left of the target

Title: Pitch Control 25m
Description: Hit 10 pitches from 25m and stop 3 inside 3m (fairway)

Title: Lag Putting 15m
Description: Hit 3 putts inside 2 meters of the hole from 15 meters

Title: 2m Around The Hole
Description: Make 4 putts around the hole from 2 meters

Title: Chip 15m Fairway
Description: Hit 10 chip shots from 15m and get at least 3 shots to stop within 2 meters of the hole (Fairway)

Title: Chip 15m Rough
Description: Hit 10 chip shots from 15m and get at least 3 shots to stop within 3 meters of the hole (Rough)

Title: Trajectory Challenge 100m
Description: Hit 3 high shots and 3 low shots to the 100m target

Title: Putt Test 1m
Description: Make 10 putts around the hole in a row from 1 meter

Title: Strike Quality 150m
Description: Hit 3 consecutive clean shots that land past the 150 meter target
